<div class="wrapper">
  <h2 class="pm-places-header">
    Precautionary Measures
  </h2>
  <hr class="section-hr mt-0 mb-0">
  <div class="section mt-3">
    <div class="container pm-places-container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <p>Bolo Kobul is committed to a safer internet and go great lengths to ensure you get the best
            possible experience. Every single profile is screened for irrelevant and inappropriate content
            and your matches are suggested as per your preferences.</p>
          <p>While we do our part, we want you to play yours. Please read the precautionary measures in
            order to have a safe and enjoyable match-making experience.</p>
          <div id="accordion" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true" class="card-collapse">
            <%= render partial: 'precautionary_measure',
                       collection: @precautionary_measures %>
          </div>
          <p>If you observe anything suspicious <a href="/contact">write to us</a>.</p>
          <p><u><b>
            Please note: Bolo Kobul will NEVER ask you for money outside of the platform. If someone claims
            to be from Bolo Kobul and asks you to send money via any mobile finance services or in person, please
            know it is not us. We only accept debit and credit card payments made through the platform only.
          </b></u></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-50"></div>
</div>
